<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-779] Cannot enrich from a source property of type OMText</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-779</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Say we have the following configuration to extract a text as a property. &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;enrich&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;source clone=&quot;true&quot; &lt;br/&gt;
           xpath=&quot;//foo/bar/a/text()&quot; /&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;target type=&quot;property&quot; property=&quot;TEXT_VAL&quot;/&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/enrich&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now we cannot enrich from the property we extracted from above enrich mediator. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;enrich&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;source type=&quot;property&quot; property=&quot;TEXT_VAL&quot;/&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;target xpath=&quot;//a/bar/c/text()&quot;/&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/enrich&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
